.TH list 1  "list " 
.SH NAME
list \- List all collections
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBlist\fR [\fB\-\-bookmark\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
List all collections
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-bookmark\fR \fI<BOOKMARK>\fR
List collections containing this bookmark
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
